jsymbolic2.processing

Class FeatureExtractorAccess

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsymbolic2.featureutils.FeatureExtractorAccess

  • public final class FeatureExtractorAccess
extends java.lang.Object
    A central access point to obtain all feature information, where features are accessible in the correct order with respect to the boolean array for features to save. This allows for consistent comparisons of all the input features from any source, i.e. command line, gui or configuration file.
